command_group: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup project

commands.name: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup project list
commands.summary: List GitLab projects that are directly owned by given group and onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup project list --group-name
                                                               --name
                                                               --resource-group
                                                               [--max-items]
                                                               [--next-token]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup project show
commands.summary: Get a monitored GitLab Project resource for a given fully-qualified group name and project name.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup project show [--group-name]
                                                               [--ids]
                                                               [--name]
                                                               [--project-name]
                                                               [--resource-group]
                                                               [--subscription]
